Class MainActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • ca.ualberta.cs.queueunderflow.views.MainActivity

  • public class MainActivity
extends Activity
    The Class MainActivity. Handles clicks & swipes relating to switching between fragments via the navigation drawer. Also handles calling the load/save functions.
